videos.description: Steph Curry hits two impressive 3-pointers early in the first quarter as the Warriors take on the Celtics.

videos.headline: Steph heats up from downtown early vs. Celtics

videos.description: Jabari Parker makes his debut with the Celtics and puts down an easy clean-up dunk inside.

videos.headline: Parker scores first points as a Celtic

videos.description: Jayson Tatum gets the ball with the clock winding down and sinks the buzzer-beater while falling away from the basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum beats buzzer while falling away) 2021//4 17ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum beats buzzer while falling away

videos.description: Steph Curry drains a wild and-1 step-back jumper and Kemba Walker races down the court to bank in an out of control transition layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry, Kemba hit wild circus shots in the first half) 2021/04/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Curry, Kemba hit wild circus shots in the first half

videos.description: Marcus Smart gets the steal and tosses a long-distance pass to Jayson Tatum who goes up to flush a powerful dunk on the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smart's steal sets up Tatum fast-break slam) 2021/04/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smart's steal sets up Tatum fast-break slam

videos.description: Kemba Walker sinks a big-time 3-pointer to put the Celtics up five in the final minute.

videos.headline: Kemba drains clutch 3 down the stretch

videos.description: Juan Toscano-Anderson takes a nasty tumble over the scores table on the sidelines as he attempts to save a loose ball. He would eventually walk off the floor under his own power.

videos.headline: Toscano-Anderson takes scary tumble over scorers table

videos.description: The Celtics continue their winning ways behind Jayson Tatum's 44 points and 10 rebounds as they pick up a hard-fought 119-114 win against the Warriors.

videos.headline: Tatum's 44-point double-double leads Celtics in thriller vs. Warriors

videos.description: Steph Curry breaks out into a dance after he splashes yet another 3-pointer to help the Warriors regain the lead vs. the Celtics.
